---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About me"
  description="Minimalizt Dev Blog - posts about software development"
  pubDate={new Date("March 26 2025")}
>
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="profile-section">
      <img
        class="profile-image"
        src="/pp.jpeg"
        alt="Profile Picture"
        height={300}
        width={300}
      />
    </div>

    <div class="bio-section">
      <h2>Hello, I'm Nico!</h2>

      <p>
        I’m a full-stack product engineer and engineering leader with 8+ years
        of experience building and scaling customer-facing applications across
        web, mobile, and microservices. I’m passionate about developer
        productivity, building software with measurable product outcomes, and
        generative AI.
      </p>

      <p>
        Currently, I'm leading a team of 9 software engineers at <a
          href="https://swapfiets.nl/en-nl"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Swapfiets</a
        >.
      </p>

      <p>
        This blog is where I share my thoughts and experiences about software
        development, AI, and technical leadership.
      </p>

      <p>
        In my free time, I'm hacking on a few side projects. Check it out here:

        <ul>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://turboform.ai"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              TurboForm
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://supermeme.ai"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              Supermeme.ai
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </p>
      <div class="connect-section">
        <h3>Let's connect</h3>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or feedback feel free to reach out on
          <a href="https://x.com/nwbotha" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X</a> or
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nico-botha"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a
          >.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .profile-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .profile-image {
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 3px solid #f5f5f5;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .bio-section {
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .bio-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  .bio-section h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    color: #444;
  }

  .bio-section p {
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    color: #444;
  }

  .connect-section {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .social-links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .social-links li {
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }

  .social-links a {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    color: #333;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .social-links a:hover {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .profile-image {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>
